OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779984666
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cwho died at West Yorkshire reservoir
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a 13-year-
OL,7,Fold who died after getting into
OL,8,Fdifficulty in a reservoir, with a
OL,9,Frugby club saying there are "just no
OL,10,Fwords (...) for such tragedies".
OL,12,FPolice were called to Leadbeater Dam
OL,13,Fon Lumb Lane, Halifax, just before
OL,14,F3.20pm on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,16,FReco Puttock, was pulled from the
OL,17,Fwater and taken to hospital where he
OL,18,Fwas pronounced dead, officers said.
OL,26,@rD@GpmrD@Kpn
