OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779984666
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cwho died at West Yorkshire reservoir
OL,6,FKing Cross Park Rugby League Club, in
OL,7,FHalifax, said in a statement:
OL,8,F"Yesterday we were informed of the
OL,9,Fdevastating news that Reco Puttock,
OL,10,Fwho played for our 2025 U13s,
OL,11,Ftragically lost his life.
OL,13,F"There are no words we can say which
OL,14,Fwill make this loss any less painful
OL,15,Ffor his family and friends especially
OL,16,Fat such a young age.
OL,18,F"So, on behalf of the entire club, we
OL,19,Fwould like to extend our thoughts and
OL,20,Fcondolences with his family, friends
OL,21,Fand team mates.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779984666
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cwho died at West Yorkshire reservoir
OL,6,F"Rest in peace young man."
OL,8,FAnother club, Kippax Welfare Rugby
OL,9,FLeague, said on social media: "On
OL,10,Fbehalf of everyone associated with
OL,11,FKippax Welfare we offer our heartfelt
OL,12,Fcondolences to the family, friends,
OL,13,Floved ones of Reco and everyone at
OL,14,FKing Cross Park ARLFC.
OL,16,F"There are just no words befitting for
OL,17,Fsuch tragedies, in times of
OL,18,Funimaginable grief, rivalries and
OL,19,Fcolours simply do not matter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779984666
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cwho died at West Yorkshire reservoir
OL,6,F"Rugby league has lost one of its own
OL,7,Fand we grieve as one.
OL,9,F"RIP Reco, may you be forever
OL,10,Fremembered, loved and cherished in the
OL,11,Fmemories of all those who's lives you
OL,12,Fblessed."
OL,14,FLightcliffe Academy, in Halifax, also
OL,15,Fissued a statement which said: "We are
OL,16,Fdeeply saddened by the death of one of
OL,17,Four students, Reco.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779984666
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' teenager
OL,4,Cwho died at West Yorkshire reservoir
OL,6,F"Reco was a popular and much-loved
OL,7,Fstudent who will be greatly missed by
OL,8,Fstudents, staff and our wider academy
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts, prayers and condolences
OL,12,Fgo out to his family, and all affected
OL,13,Fby this tragic loss at this incredibly
OL,14,Fdifficult time."
OL,16,FThe school said support is available
OL,17,Fto students both now and as they
OL,18,Freturn after half-term.
OL,20,FIt said that information will follow
OL,21,Fregarding plans to pay tribute to Reco.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
